Class Enemy

java.lang.Object
Enemy
Direct Known Subclasses:
Boss
public class Enemy extends Object
Enemy class to create enemy instances with specific attributes. Each enemy has a type, name, health, attack, and defense values. It also handles enemy spawning and initialization of enemy stats.
